# Backstop only: dirs accidentally named after a Python dict repr
# (e.g. ``{Em1: 1.0, …}/``).  The root cause is fixed in pipeline/save.py
# (params_slug + _sanitize_output_path slugify any params dict that
# reaches an output path), so this should no longer trigger; kept as a
# safety net.  Regenerable.
{*}/

# Reference papers (local only — copyrighted, not redistributed in the repo)
Literature/

# Public repo = pipeline code + tests + new-user docs (the README files) + the
# curated notebooks. Everything below stays local but is not tracked / shipped.
